    <item>
      <title>尽管抛售 45 亿美元，特朗普仍有望获得 SPAC 额外发薪日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/trump-in-line-for-extra-spac-payday-despite-4-5-billion-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普媒体公司的开局并不顺利。科技集团公司 (Technology Group Corp.) 的股价在短短几周内就蒸发了 45 亿美元的市值。但它必须损失的远不止于此，才能将前总统及其公司内部人士的巨额特别奖金置于危险之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/trump-in-line-for-extra-spac-payday-despite-4-5-billion-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 15:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列人在等待伊朗导弹的同时忙着自己的事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/israelis-go-about-their-business-as-they-await-iranian-missiles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他们没有取消特拉维夫戈登海滩长廊上的免费民间舞蹈，周六有数百人参加。沐浴时微风徐徐，但地平线上布满了帆，骑自行车的人在自行车道上巡游，摆着海边早午餐的桌子已经满了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/israelis-go-about-their-business-as-they-await-iranian-missiles</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 14:14:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国将向乌克兰提供另一套爱国者反导系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/germany-to-give-ukraine-another-patriot-anti-missile-system</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰将从德国接收另一套爱国者导弹防御系统和弹药，这些设备是该国在电网遭受数次严重袭击后迫切需要的设备，以加强抵御俄罗斯导弹袭击的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/germany-to-give-ukraine-another-patriot-anti-missile-system</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗在霍尔木兹海峡附近扣押与以色列有关的集装箱船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/iran-s-irgc-seizes-israel-linked-container-ship-near-hormuz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国营伊斯兰共和国通讯社报道，伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队周六在波斯湾和阿曼湾之间的霍尔木兹海峡附近扣押了一艘与以色列有关的集装箱船。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/iran-s-irgc-seizes-israel-linked-container-ship-near-hormuz</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 10:54:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《华尔街日报》称普京计划重启被扣押的乌克兰核电站</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/putin-aims-to-restart-seized-ukrainian-nuclear-plant-wsj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》报道，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京告诉联合国原子能机构，俄罗斯计划重启乌克兰东南部的扎波罗热核电站，俄罗斯军队已占领该核电站两年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/putin-aims-to-restart-seized-ukrainian-nuclear-plant-wsj-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 09:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度启动夏季燃气发电厂运行紧急规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/india-invokes-emergency-rules-to-run-gas-power-plants-for-summer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着电力需求开始上升，印度援引一项紧急条款，命令其闲置的燃气发电站在夏季运行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/india-invokes-emergency-rules-to-run-gas-power-plants-for-summer</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 09:07:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗革命卫队在霍尔木兹海峡附近扣押集装箱船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-13/urgent-british-military-warns-of-possible-vessel-being-boarded-near-strait-of-hormuz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国迪拜（美联社）——伊朗准军事革命卫队的突击队周六从直升机上垂降到霍尔木兹海峡附近的一艘以色列附属集装箱船上，并扣押了该船，这是两国之间一系列袭击事件中的最新一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-13/urgent-british-military-warns-of-possible-vessel-being-boarded-near-strait-of-hormuz</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 08:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MSC 表示，巴尔的摩灾难中的托运人面临“共同海损”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/baltimore-bridge-companies-with-goods-on-ship-on-the-hook-for-damages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据世界领先的集装箱运输公司称，摧毁巴尔的摩弗朗西斯斯科特基大桥的船主已启动一项正式程序，在受灾大理上拥有货物的公司将不得不分担部分财务损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/baltimore-bridge-companies-with-goods-on-ship-on-the-hook-for-damages</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 07:45:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯质疑杜特尔特与中国就海洋争端达成的“秘密”协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/marcos-questions-secret-duterte-deal-with-china-on-sea-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯表示，他的前任罗德里戈·杜特尔特与北京就南海争端达成的“君子协议”是故意向公众隐瞒的。]]></description>
